            "sidebarText": "<h3 class=\"title\">Corrupted Pegasi</h3>When a foul influence from the fiendish planes, a necromantic blight, or any other sinister influence spreads through a wilderness, pegasi can become corrupted. These neutral evil pegasi have the same statistics as those presented here, but are much more violent.",
